[I] Plasma Login Manager

[T] Plasma Login provides a display manager for KDE Plasma, forked from SDDM
[T] and with an new frontend providing a greeter, wallpaper plugin integration
[T] and System Settings module (KCM).

[U] https://invent.kde.org/plasma/plasma-login-manager

